        I'm a front-end engineer with solid experience in designing, building
        usable, maintainable interfaces. With experience in front-end
        development and always eager to learn new things, I'm confident to
        work effectively under various circumstances, either self-managed in
        independent projects, or collaborate as part of productive teams.
      </p>
    </section>
    <div class="h-8 w-8"></div>
    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-3xl">Technical Skills</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        <span class="text-gray-900 text-lg">Programing languagues:</span>
        JavaScript, TypeScript, Clojure(script)
        <br />
        <span class="text-gray-900 text-lg">Web development:</span>
        HTML, CSS, Tailwind CSS
        <br />
        <span class="text-gray-900 text-lg">Front-end framework:</span>
        React, Next.js
        <br />
        <span class="text-gray-900 text-lg"
        >Miscellaneous:</span
        >
        Node.js, Git, Docker, Unix, Vim,...
        <br />
      </p>
    </section>
    <div class="h-8 w-8"></div>
    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-3xl">Education</h1>
      <section class="flex items-baseline">
        <section>
          <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900">
            University of Information Technology
          </h3>
          <ul>
            <li class="text-gray-600">
              Engineer's degree in network & communication system
            </li>
            <li class="text-gray-600">
              Gpa: 7.0/10; Undergraduate, est. 2022
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="ml-auto text-right text-gray-600 flex-grow">
          <p>National University, Hồ Chí Minh</p>
          <p>2018-now</p>
        </section>
      </section>
      <section class="flex items-baseline">
        <section>
          <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900">Gia Định highschool</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Specialized class in computer science</p>
        </section>
        <section class="ml-auto text-right text-gray-600">
          <p>Hồ Chí Minh city</p>
          <p>2015-2018</p>
        </section>
      </section>
    </section>
    <div class="h-8 w-8"></div>
