        <ul class="list-disc list-outside px-8">
          <li>
            Front-end Development:
            <span class="text-gray-600"
            >Maintain existing production applications, handle production
              incidents and build new features for the application
            </span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Notable works:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-outside px-8">
          <li>
            Chat center:
            <span class="text-gray-600"
            >Maintainer, built upon WebSocket, helps bridge the gap of
              communication between customers and be's services</span
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            Call center:
            <span class="text-gray-600"
            >Main developer/maintainer, a combination between WebRTC and
              Websocket to provide another way to receiving feedback from
              customers</span
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </section>
    <div class="h-8 w-8"></div>
    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-3xl">Projects & Contributions</h1>
      <section>
        <ul class="list-disc px-4">
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://violeine.github.io/daphDVD"
              class="text-xl text-blue-600 visited:text-indigo-600"
            >daphdvd:</a
            >
            <span class="text-gray-600"
            >Intro screen for streamer
              <a
                class="text-blue-600 visited:text-indigo-600"
                href="https://twitch.tv/39daph"
              >39daph</a
              >
              on twitch.tv.</span
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/violeine/fu.nc"
              class="text-xl text-blue-600 visited:text-indigo-600"
            >fu.nc:</a
            >
