              create rounded favicon from Github.</span
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/violeine/re.sume"
              class="text-xl text-blue-600 visited:text-indigo-600"
            >re.sume:</a
            >
            <span class="text-gray-600"
            >Resume built with tailwindcss, print-ready, support export to
              pdf through nextjs api function.</span
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/moaijs/moai"
              class="text-xl text-blue-600 visited:text-indigo-600"
            >Moai</a
            >
            &
            <a
              href="https://github.com/beVietnam/banhmi"
              class="text-xl text-blue-600 visited:text-indigo-600"
            >Bánh Mì:</a
            >
